\subsection{Generalized quaternion}
\begin{definition}\label{group.generalized_quaternion}
\uses{group.dicyclic}
The **(generalized) quaternion group** $Q_n$ is a special case of a {{ KNOWL("group.dicyclic", "dicyclic")}} group $\text{Dic}_m$ when $n=4m\geq 8$ is a power of $2$. 
\end{definition}


